				Hi all, just a few things i've found about these ghouls:<BR>
<BR>
-There's at least three places they spawn: two just inside the side porch door, and one in a tiny alcove by the entrance to the roundroom (on the OUTSIDE of the house, bad spot for them IMO). Didn't go upstairs to find out if they spawn anywhere else.  <BR>
-I don't recall them ever attempting to root, but they did hit rather hard.<BR>
-They conned blue to me at 31.  <BR>
-Drops were nothing special, no bronze or fine steel.<BR>

